---
import ButtonPlayStore from '../ButtonPlayStore.astro'
import Crown from '../icons/Crown.astro'
import Navbar from '../Navbar.astro'
---

<header class='header_bg w-screen relative h-screen max-sm:h-auto bg-dark'>
  <Navbar />
  <section
    class='mx-auto w-[70%] max-sm:w-full relative items-center p-10 justify-center flex flex-col'
  >
    <Crown
      stroke='#ffff'
      class='absolute top-0 left-[26%] max-sm:left-[10%] -rotate-12'
    />
    <h1
      class='font-Baloo text-[50px] max-sm:text-4xl max-md:text-5xl text-center font-extrabold mt-4 uppercase'
    >
      Bienvenido a <strong
        class='font-Baloo font-extrabold bg-clip-text text-transparent linear'
        >Hobby</strong
      >
    </h1>
    <p
      class='w-[50%] mt-5 max-sm:w-full max-md:w-[80%] max-sm:text-base max-sm:mt-10 text-lg text-center text-white/60'
    >
      ¡Comparte tus pasiones con el mundo y conéctate con millones de personas a
      través de tus pasatiempos favoritos! <strong class='font-bold text-white'
        >¡Descarga nuestra aplicación muy pronto!</strong
      >
    </p>
    <div
      class='w-[70%] flex items-center justify-center text-center mt-10 max-sm:mt-8'
    >
      <ButtonPlayStore />
    </div>
  </section>
</header>

<style>
  .header_bg {
    background-image: url(/linear-gradient/linear-header.webp);
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-position: center;
    background-size: cover;
  }
  .linear {
    background: linear-gradient(to left, #8700c7, #f97124, #f9d423);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
  }
</style>
